Pinnacle has partnered with MyBroadband to launch a Windows 7 upgrade survey. The survey will only take 2 minutes to complete, and will provide valuable insight into the use of Windows 7 in local companies. By taking part in the survey, you also stand a chance to win great prizes. The prizes up for grabs are a Wi-Fi repeater and a Bluetooth speaker. Once you have completed the survey, state “Done” in this forum thread to enter the giveaway. Standard competition rules apply.